                                                    ThumbType="???"
                                                    ThumbImage="missionMilestoneMedia/mission9/milestone2Thumbnail.png"
                                                    PopupTitle="MILITARY WITHDRAWAL"
                                                    PopupSubtitle="3. THE A400Ms ACHIEVE THE MISSION MORE EFFECTIVELY AND AT A LOWER COST"
                                                    PopupMediaFile="missionMilestoneMedia/mission9/MILITARYWITHDRAWAL-03-AchieveTheMission.wmv"
                                                    PopupDescriptionHeading="LOWER LIFE CYCLE COSTS AND HIGHER PRODUCTIVITY"
                                                    PopupDescriptionBody="Thanks to its superior performance and capabilities, a fleet of 8 A400Ms offers the same productivity as a fleet of 18 previous generation tactical airlifters. The life cycle cost of these 18 previous generation tactical airlifters is 55% higher than the one of the 8 A400Ms." />

